Lore: Despite the misfortunes surrounding her and the chaos that she appears in, she is a source of reassurance and comfort. Tenebrous is a valiant warrior who will not stand for cruelty and will take on the evils that threaten the innocent, even at the possibility of her own death. She has slain a few higher powered entities and been further ostracized due to the power and ability she's shown to wipe even non-mortal existence away with cold, pure intention.

Other: Tenebrous is a shapeshifting entity, often taking form to better fit into the universe she's traversing. Whether feral or human, humanoid, or monster, her appearance is always dark with golden accents and armor and glowing white eyes. The amount of eyes/wings may vary on animal/monster, but human/humanoid will always have 6 wings, 6 sets of horns, and 2 eyes.
